character.description: One of Senjougahara's most attractive features is her mind. She is smart, intelligent, and highly knowledgeable. She is well-read and has a love of learning. Her mind is like a sponge and she absorbs information and knowledge like there is no tomorrow. She is well-respected and admired by others and they enjoy listening to her talk.
